{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Ricotta","content":["Place milk in mixing bowl and heat <nobr>10 min\/80°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Add vinegar and heat <nobr>3 min\/90°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Milk will separate into curds and whey. Leave to sit in mixing bowl for 1 minute.","Line simmering basket with a nut milk bag or 2 layers of muslin cloth and set over a large jug. Gently pour ricotta into lined simmering basket and leave to drain for 15 minutes.","Stir salt through ricotta, then transfer into a bowl and set aside to cool. Clean and dry mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Pancakes","content":["Place courgette in mixing bowl and grate <nobr>5 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Transfer grated courgette into simmering basket and drain off any excess liquid. Transfer into a separate bowl to ricotta and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place spring onion\/shallot in mixing bowl and chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butter and cook <nobr>1 min 30 sec\/60°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add flour, buttermilk, salt, pepper, and eggs then mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add corn, 90 g reserved ricotta and reserved grated courgette then combine <nobr>10 sec\/\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","To cook pancakes, place a medium-sized non-stick frying pan over medium heat and add ½ tsp butter into pan.","For each pancake, pour in a ladle of batter and cook 1-2 minutes or until bubbles start bursting on pancake surface, then flip pancake and cook for a further 1 minute.","Transfer into a thermal serving bowl or warm ceramic dish and cover with a kitchen towel to keep warm. Repeat with remaining batter to make 10 pancakes. Serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Ricotta","content":["1500 g whole milk","40 g white vinegar","¼ tsp fine sea salt"]},{"title":"Pancakes","content":["310 g courgette (approx. 1), cut into pieces","1 spring onion\/shallot, white part only","40 g butter, plus extra for frying","170 g self-raising flour","200 g buttermilk","¼ tsp fine sea salt","¼ tsp ground black pepper","2 eggs","130 g fresh corn kernels"]}],"id":"r123589","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-AUfUAyt5hts\/XZVRV0Fq8TI\/AAAAAAAAdNI\/SmhZGbtBB9k4WftVCV1kLLhEnm1N75V_wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_m2H3hkXuuGI7aZYQ.png","title":"Courgette, Corn and Ricotta Pancakes","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"10 g","fat":"14 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"25 g","calories":"1149 kJ \/ 273 kcal"},"usefulItems":"muslin or nut milk bag, large jug, 2 bowls, frying pan, medium-sized non-stick frying pan, turner \/ fish slice, ladle, thermal serving bowl or warm ceramic dish, tea towel, hob","hintsAndTricks":["Serve pancakes with extra ricotta and your favourite toppings, such as chopped tomatoes or sweet chilli sauce."],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","1h 5m","1 total recipe"]}